# Implementation Plan - Remove #tags Feature (UI Only)

The goal is to remove the "Wrap Up" tags input from the [TodayScreen](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart#17-25). The underlying data model and other features (search, export, analysis) will retain support for tags to preserve backward compatibility and support existing data.

## Proposed Changes

### UI Layer

#### [MODIFY] [today_screen.dart](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart)
- Remove `_tagsController`.
- Remove "Tags" text field from [_buildActionsPage](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart#645-802).
- Remove tag saving logic in [_autoSave](file:///Users/aniruddhmodi/Documents/Aniruddh/Extracurricular/flutter-app/the_30sec_journal/lib/screens/today_screen.dart#84-122) (new entries will have empty tags).

